由於鐳具有放射性，因此在現今的用途並不廣。但鐳在過去有著許多應用。鐳曾經常用於發光塗料中<ref name="PMC2024184">{{cite journal|title=Radium in the healing arts and in industry: Radiation exposure in the United States|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_public-health-reports_1954-03_69_3/page/255|pmc=2024184|year=1954|volume=69|issue=3|pmid=13134440|last1=Terrill Jr|first1=JG|last2=Ingraham Sc|first2=2nd|last3=Moeller|first3=DW|pages=255–62|journal=Public Health Reports|doi=10.2307/4588736|jstor=4588736}}</ref>，無知的人們甚至經常將鐳添加到[[飲用水|飲用水]]、[[牙膏|牙膏]]和許多其他產品中，認為放射線可以促進健康，直到他們發現放射線對人體的致命危害時才逐漸停止使用。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.radford.edu/~wkovarik/envhist/radium.html |title=Mass Media & Environmental Conflict – Radium Girls |accessdate=2009-08-01 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090721113733/http://www.radford.edu/~wkovarik/envhist/radium.html |archivedate=2009-07-21 }}</ref><ref name="Gray">{{cite book|last=Gray|first=Theodore|authorlink=Theodore Gray|title=The Elements: A Visual Exploration of Every Known Atom in the Universe|url=https://archive.org/details/elementsvisualex0000gray|year=2009|publisher=Black Dog & Leventhal Publishers|location=New York|isbn=978-1-57912-814-2}}</ref>現今鐳被少量地用作工業及醫療上的[[放射源|放射源]]，但也多被其他更強大且更安全的放射性同位素所取代。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3cT2REdXJ98C&pg=PA24 |page=24 |title=Radiation source use and replacement: Abbreviated version |isbn=978-0-309-11014-3 |last1=Committee On Radiation Source Use And Replacement |first1=National Research Council (U.S.) |last2=Nuclear And Radiation Studies Board |first2=National Research Council (U.S.) |date=January 2008 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905164805/https://books.google.com/books?id=3cT2REdXJ98C&pg=PA24 |archivedate=2015-09-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bk0go_-FO5QC&pg=PA8 |pages=8 |title=Radiation therapy planning |isbn=978-0-07-005115-7 |last1=Bentel |first1=Gunilla Carleson |year=1996 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905174312/https://books.google.com/books?id=bk0go_-FO5QC&pg=PA8 |archivedate=2015-09-05 }}</ref>

== 在生物圈的位置 ==
*鈹的低水溶性令其難以被生物利用，而且鈹和其化合物都有劇毒。<ref name=deGruyter>{{cite book
 | others = trans. rev. Eagleson, Mary
 | editor1-first = Hans-Dieter | editor1-last=Jakubke
 | editor2-first = Hans | editor2-last = Jeschkeit
 | title = Concise Encyclopedia Chemistry
 | publisher = Walter de Gruyter
 | location = Berlin
 | year = 1994}}</ref>此外，鈹及其化合物更已被[[國際癌症研究機構|國際癌症研究機構]]列為[[1類致癌物|1類致癌物]]。
*鎂和鈣在生物圈較為普及，並佔有重要的位置。它們參與多種角色，如鎂/鈣離子就參與一些生物細胞中的作用；鎂作為某些[[酶|酶]]的活性中心；鈣鹽（如[[羥磷灰石|羥磷灰石]]）則是構成生物結構的成份之一，如[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]的[[骨骼|骨骼]]就含有鈣鹽。
*鍶和鋇在生物圈內的可用性較低。鍶在[[海洋|海洋]]生物，特別是在硬[[珊瑚|珊瑚]]扮演較重要的角色；牠們以鍶建立外骨骼。這兩種元素都有其醫學用途，如[[硫酸鋇|硫酸鋇]]就是使用[[X光|X光]]透視腸胃前需服用的藥物。鍶化合物則可應用於[[牙膏|牙膏]]中。
*鐳的可用性較低，並有著高放射性，因此它對生物來說是劇毒的。

